 2025年奥斯卡将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-soscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-eriginal-original-song-category-3831285？utm_source = rsss = rsss＆utm_medium = rsssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssm_campairntim=--奥斯卡奖将不包括最佳基础类别的绩效Surej SinghThu, 23 Jan 2025 07:30:47 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3831285 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>取而代之的是，仪式将探索“使这些歌曲栩栩如生的团队的个人思考”</p><p> 2025年奥斯卡颁奖<a href="https://www.nme.com">典礼</a>的帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/oscars@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">2025年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼</a>将远离其传统的计划。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/kneecap-film-review-biopic-michael-fassbender-3779661">“ Kneecap”评论：Ballsy，Brave和有史以来最好的音乐传记之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscar-nominations-postponed-again-due-to-california-wildfires-3828870">今天晚些时候（1月23日）透露奥斯卡的核心提名</a>之前，美国电影艺术与科学学院首席执行官珍妮特·杨（Janet Yang）和比尔·克莱默。</p><p>每个<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/2025-oscar-ceremony-best-original-song-presentations-move-away-from-live-performances-1235881065/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>广告牌</em></a>，今年3月2日的仪式将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的现场表演。通常，在类别中提名的艺术家将在颁奖典礼上整夜演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3598768" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3598768" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3598768" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch.jpg" alt="奥斯卡奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Oscars-2024-how-to-watch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598768" class="wp-caption-text">奥斯卡。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>杨和克莱默在给<em>学院</em>成员的信中写道：“今年，最好的原创歌曲类别演示将摆脱现场表演，并将专注于词曲作者。我们将通过将这些歌曲变为现实的团队的个人反思来庆祝他们的艺术才华。所有这些以及更多内容都将揭开今年提名者背后的故事和灵感。”</p><p>此外，杨和克莱默还指出，今年的仪式将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">本月早些时候进行毁灭性的野火</a>之后，包括洛杉矶的特别纪念。行业。”</p><p>虽然大多数奥斯卡提名将在今天晚些时候透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/elton-john-pharrell-williams-trent-reznor-among-oscars-2025-shortlist-for-best-original-song-3823258">但最佳原创歌曲和最佳原创乐谱的入围名单在12月揭幕</a>。在最佳原创歌曲入围名单的艺术家中，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">Pharrell Williams</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trent-reznor">Trent Reznor</a>和Atticus Ross， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>等。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="在Reading＆Leeds 2024赢得奥斯卡奖和Fontaines D.C." width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/64_mPMu-v2s?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）</a>的“禁忌之路”（Robbie Williams）的传记片<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/better-man"><em>《更好的人</em></a>》也被包括在候选名单中，尽管后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-forbidden-road-disqualified-from-oscars-shortlist-3824206">被取消了这部电影的“现有歌曲中的材料”的资格</a>。</p><p>同时，几个主要的大片在入围名单中获得了最佳原始得分的评分。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>邪恶的</em></a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2"><em>角斗士2</em></a> ，<em>挑战者</em>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/beetlejuice-beetlejuice"><em>Beetlejuice Beetlejuice</em></a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/alien-romulus"><em>Alien：Romulus</em></a>等。</p><p> 2025年奥斯卡颁奖<a href="https://www.nme.com">典礼</a>的帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的表演</a>。</p> ;
